  "html": "\n<h4></h4>\n\n<a href=\"/metrs.php?id=147&amp;type=tvorch\" class=\"redhr1\">Творчість</a> |\n<a href=\"/metrs.php?id=147&amp;type=biogr\" class=\"redhr1\">Біографія</a> |\n<a href=\"/metrs.php?id=147&amp;type=critiques\" class=\"redhr1\">Критика</a>\n\n<h4>Дощ</h4>\n<!--<div style=\"float:right;margin-left: 10px\">\n\t<script async src=\"//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js\"></script>\n\n\t<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\n\t\t style=\"display:inline-block;width:250px;height:400px\"\n\t\t data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5357335372099528\"\n\t\t data-ad-slot=\"7581761695\"></ins>\n\t<script>\n\t(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n\t</script>\n</div>-->\n\nПарило. &nbsp;Нахмарило. &nbsp;<br>\nНахмурились &nbsp;дуби. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nЗамовкли &nbsp;голуби.<br>\n<br>\nІ &nbsp;смугою &nbsp;рясною &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nЗ &nbsp;раптовою &nbsp;грозою &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nПолився &nbsp;шумно &nbsp;синій &nbsp;дощ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nНа &nbsp;довгу &nbsp;скаргу &nbsp;жовтих &nbsp;площ.<br>\n<br>\nІ &nbsp;вмить &nbsp;розправили &nbsp;дуби &nbsp;<br>\nКремезні &nbsp;крона. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nГолуби &nbsp;Заворкували.І &nbsp;в &nbsp;полях &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nПовисла &nbsp;райдуга &nbsp;на &nbsp;шлях.<br>\n<br>\nА &nbsp;в &nbsp;хмарах &nbsp;- &nbsp;ширшає &nbsp;віконце, &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\nПовніє &nbsp;синє &nbsp;гронце &nbsp;- &nbsp;Сонце!<br>\n<br>\n1939<br>\n\n\n\n<br><br>\n"
}